{
  "texts": [
    "This module may enlarge the receptive field and assign different attention domains to distinct receptive fields, greatly boosting the network's feature extraction ability.",
    "(3) In order to adapt to the low-light object detection task, we substitute the original detection head with a decoupled head.",
    "At the same time, we replaced the SPPF module with the SimSPPF module, which increases the network's inference performance and feature extraction ability.",
    "(4) Compared with other state-of-the-art methods, NLE-YOLO shows good performance on the low-light dataset ExDark.",
    "There are three types of existing object detection algorithms: one-stage algorithms, two-stage algorithms, and anchor-free methods."
